message.body: That house would be a great place to go for Halloween and Harry Potter marathons!
I was at Staples. Waiting for documents to me faxed to me and tax it back. I'm just not in the mood today. Happy Friday! How's it going?
Oh I'm sorry. I hope your day got better... Ive actually been sleeping since 3, just had my eye surgery so needed to keep my eyes closed
Yeah. Needed to correct my eyes a bit.
Is everything okay? Was it last minute/emergency?
Nah... I needed a touch up because my vision for a bit worse. Everything's good.
Are you going to have to keep touching up every once in a while?
Nah... Just this time. Has a change in vision. Hopefully I won't have to do it again.
